data.description: $10K PRICE REDUCTION! Owner is packed and ready to move to Florida!  Open House SATURDAY 10A-12P & SUNDAY 2P-4P! $0.00 Down / 100% FINANCING AVAILABLE!  1% Rate Buydown also Available! Contact Listing Agent for more details. Country living but close to the city! Lots of space in this beautiful one level home with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths. The updated kitchen has granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and easy to clean tile. Hardwood floors in the living area along with updated tile bathrooms. The roof is approximately 5 years old. There is so much potential at a very affordable price. The oversized lot gives you a little over an acre of land with plenty of room for entertaining or your animals to run. You have a tree house already standing by for the kids and so much room to play. All of this while still being very convenient to downtown Jeffersonville! Come out and make this your new home today!  Initial 2 photos are from Owner's purchase July -2021. Owner has had trouble getting a contractor out to do the pressure washing / cleaning / staining along with bush trimming to make it look like that again. Will update exterior pictures at that time. UPDATE: Owner making a price reduction to encourage a quick sale.
